这是毒药?
I exhibited the Devil's foot.

776
00:47:15,196 --> 00:47:16,891
难以置信
Poison you say?

777
00:47:16,965 --> 00:47:19,297
你没试过不会相信的
Fascinating.

778
00:47:19,368 --> 00:47:21,562
一点点就能够致命
You wouldn't think so if you were to try it.

779
00:47:21,637 --> 00:47:23,365
这种粉末
The smallest amount could be fatal.

780
00:47:23,437 --> 00:47:26,633
在燃烧时会即刻反应
In this powder form

781
00:47:26,707 --> 00:47:28,334
刺激大脑中枢
it reacts instantaneously when burned.

782
00:47:28,409 --> 00:47:31,401
控制恐惧情感的区域
It stimulates those brain centers,

783
00:47:31,479 --> 00:47:34,538
非疯即死
which control the emotion of fear.

784
00:47:34,614 --> 00:47:36,878
那些不幸的本地人
Madness or death

785
00:47:36,951 --> 00:47:38,975
若是遭受部落医师的折磨
is the fate of the unfortunate native

786
00:47:39,052 --> 00:47:41,316
就是这样的下场
who is subjected to the ordeal

787
00:47:41,388 --> 00:47:43,878
会被发现吗?
by the priest of his tribe.

788
00:47:43,957 --> 00:47:47,585
欧洲科学是不能的
Can it be detected?

789
00:47:47,661 --> 00:47:49,094
几天后
Not by European science.

790
00:47:49,161 --> 00:47:51,254
我的住处有人闯空门
A few days later

791
00:47:51,331 --> 00:47:53,890
但貌似什么都没拿
my cottage was broken into

792
00:47:53,966 --> 00:47:55,796
我没有留意
but since nothing seemed to have been taken

793
00:47:55,868 --> 00:47:57,664
直到Roudhay先生的电报
I gave the matter no heed

794
00:47:57,735 --> 00:47:59,635
到达Plymouth
until Mr. Roundhay's telegram

795
00:47:59,705 --> 00:48:03,231
Mortimer这个恶棍
arrived at Plymouth.

796
00:48:03,308 --> 00:48:04,774
以为我得知消息的时候
This villain, Mortimer,

797
00:48:04,842 --> 00:48:06,571
已经在海上
had thought that I would be at sea

798
00:48:06,645 --> 00:48:10,478
并一去非洲很多年
before news reached me,

799
00:48:10,548 --> 00:48:13,539
但我当然立刻回来
and that I should be lost for years in Africa.

800
00:48:13,618 --> 00:48:16,177
我一听到详细情况
But of course I returned immediately

801
00:48:16,253 --> 00:48:18,483
就能断定
and I could not hear the details

802
00:48:18,556 --> 00:48:21,588
他用的正是我的毒药
without being assured that it was my poison, which had been used,

803
00:48:22,189 --> 00:48:25,224
而Mortimer Tregennis本人
and that Mortimer Tregennis himself

804
00:48:25,295 --> 00:48:28,821
就是凶手
was the murderer.

805
00:48:28,898 --> 00:48:33,197
我一心要报仇
My sole cried out for revenge.

806
00:48:33,269 --> 00:48:35,794
你杀了她!
You murdered her!

807
00:48:35,871 --> 00:48:39,397
为了钱你杀了自己的亲妹妹!
For money you murdered your own sister.

808
00:48:39,475 --> 00:48:41,443
你没有证据
You can't prove that.

809
00:48:41,510 --> 00:48:43,977
当地陪审团不会相信你
No jury in the land will believe you.

810
00:48:44,046 --> 00:48:46,843
我就是陪审团 Tregennis
I'm my own jury, Mr. Tregennis.

811
00:48:46,915 --> 00:48:52,285
法官 陪审团和刽子手
Judge, jury and executioner.

812
00:49:16,542 --> 00:49:19,271
我点燃了台灯
I lit the lamp.

813
00:49:19,345 --> 00:49:21,677
把粉末放到上面
I put the powder above it.

814
00:49:38,417 --> 00:49:43,564
五分钟后他死了
In five minutes he died.

815
00:49:43,635 --> 00:49:44,554
上帝啊
My God!

816
00:49:44,591 --> 00:49:46,755
死状其惨
How he died!

817
00:49:48,472 --> 00:49:53,135
但我不为所动
But my heart was flint,

818
00:49:53,209 --> 00:49:54,869
因为他仅仅是经历了
for he endured nothing

819
00:49:54,945 --> 00:49:56,605
我无辜的心上人
which my innocent darling

820
00:49:56,681 --> 00:49:59,080
之前所经历的一切
had not suffered before him.

821
00:50:05,822 --> 00:50:10,451
你可以采取任何行动 福尔摩斯先生
You can take what steps you like, Mr. Holmes.

822
00:50:10,526 --> 00:50:13,289
但没有什么谁
But there can be no man living

823
00:50:13,362 --> 00:50:17,526
会比我现在更无惧死亡了
who fears death less than I do now.

824
00:50:25,460 --> 00:50:29,208
你原本是怎么计划的?
What where your plans?

825
00:50:29,277 --> 00:50:34,270
我打算把自己葬在中非
I was intending to bury myself in Central Africa.

826
00:50:34,349 --> 00:50:37,112
那儿的工作只进行了一半
My work there is but half done.

827
00:50:44,658 --> 00:50:47,165
那就去完成另外一半吧
Go and do the other half.

828
00:50:50,696 --> 00:50:54,722
我个人不打算阻止你
I, for one, am not prepared to stop you.

829
00:51:03,042 --> 00:51:05,532
上帝保佑你
God bless you,

830
00:51:05,611 --> 00:51:07,942
你们两位
both of you.

831
00:51:18,214 --> 00:51:21,016
已经不是第一次了 福尔摩斯
Not for the first time, Holmes,

832
00:51:21,092 --> 00:51:24,959
把法律玩弄于股掌之上
you presume to take the law into your hands.

833
00:51:28,098 --> 00:51:31,294
我从未爱过
I have never loved

834
00:51:31,368 --> 00:51:33,801
但如果有过
but if I did

835
00:51:33,870 --> 00:51:35,599
如果这个我爱的女人
and if the woman I had loved

836
00:51:35,672 --> 00:51:37,605
遭此不幸
had met with such an end

837
00:51:37,673 --> 00:51:40,038
我可能也会跟我们
I might act even as our

838
00:51:40,109 --> 00:51:44,339
无视法律的猎狮者有相同的举动
lawless lion-hunter has done.

839
00:51:44,414 --> 00:51:47,143
你不会吗?
Wouldn't you?

840
00:51:47,216 --> 00:51:50,241
嗯 可能吧
Yes, I suppose so

841
00:51:50,318 --> 00:51:51,978
但这不是关键
but that's not the point.

842
00:51:52,053 --> 00:51:55,316
关键是我为什么要做警方的工作呢?
The point is why should I do the work of the official police?

843
00:51:56,391 --> 00:51:59,052
而且正如你所言
And as your very fond of telling me,

844
00:51:59,127 --> 00:52:01,890
我在休假中
I'm on holiday!

